feat: human-readable policy numbers (PREFIX-YEAR-CODE)

Replaces the raw cuid slice (e.g. CMQIRMRJB0) shown to users with a stable,
product-aware reference like VH-2026-7K3M9Q. New helper src/utils/policyNumber.ts
derives it deterministically from id + product + createdAt year, so the same
submission renders the same number across the UI, PDF, emails, CSV export, and
the Stripe checkout line item. Applied at all 21 identifier sites; selects
extended with policyType/createdAt where needed. No DB change.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
